Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 宥姐 灼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀呵~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好…你们这么早是要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我试着邀请了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也对 四个人一起购物比较轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风好大…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宥姐姐不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了小玄…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身为姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是宥姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:03:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家长途跋涉辛苦了 接下来就四处逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么选呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是难以抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玄姐姐喜欢什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算说喜欢胸部 那么该送什么才符合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的 胸部？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宥姐每天都有供应哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实小玄她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是对胸部执着…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是始终无法忘记我们的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是在寻求母爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家里没留下多少妈妈的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「为什么不多照一些呢？」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候小玄经常很生气的这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近倒是没有这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来在儿童麻将俱乐部那时候 玄姐姐经常给我们拍照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是那 说是为了留下回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不拍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相机去年就坏掉了 所以才不拍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贺礼就决定是相机了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近能买到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么马上出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宥姐 快来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 出发~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小稳你真的是精力过剩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像是表扬的损话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有精力什么都能做到哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从龙华家公寓望出去的景色真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里 我家又没有多搞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 树枝上挂的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁不小心掉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被刮走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要掉进池子里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这下我也追不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,南无…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕 那样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回来的时候还在的话 就去叫给派出所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我的手套丢了
